Afferro Says Cameroon Tests Show Potential for Iron Ore Sinter Fines

-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-05-18T06:09:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-18/afferro-says-cameroon-tests-show-potential-for-iron-ore-sinter-fines.html
Afferro Mining Inc., the company
formerly known as African Aura Mining Inc., said metallurgical
tests at the first phase of drilling at its Nkout project in
Cameroon showed “good potential for sinter fines product.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
